verse.lines:
The Lord of my life,
He has never failed;
On my own I could never succeed.
This One I've come to know,
There's so much I owe;
And I cannot fail the Lord.

And things, when they are done,
In His Name are won;
In the past, I didn't trust God,
I trusted in myself;
Now I know I have His help,
And I cannot fail the Lord.
